=======================
doveadm-cluster-localdb
=======================


NAME
====

doveadm-cluster-localdb - Utility actions for Dovecot Cluster local cache.

.. warning:: These commands are intended for testing and debugging purposes only, they should not be normally used.


SYNOPSIS
========

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster localdb user status *group* *user*

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster localdb user list [ *mask* ]

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster localdb user remove *group* *user*

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster localdb group status *group*

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster localdb group list [ *mask* ]

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster localdb group remove *group*


DESCRIPTION
===========

**doveadm cluster localdb** can be used to run actions that interact with and
modify Dovecot Cluster local cache.

.. include:: global-options.inc

.. include:: global-options-formatter.inc


COMMANDS
========


cluster localdb user status
----------------------------

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster localdb user status *group* *user*

Displays locally cached information about a user.


cluster localdb user list
-------------------------

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster localdb user list [ *mask* ]

List users in local cache.


cluster localdb user remove
---------------------------

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster localdb user remove *group* *user*

Remove locally cached information for a user.


cluster localdb group status
----------------------------

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster localdb group status *group*

Display locally cached information about a group.


cluster localdb group list
--------------------------

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster localdb group list [ *mask* ]

List groups in local cache.


cluster localdb group remove
----------------------------

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster localdb group remove *group*

Remove locally cached information for a group.


